| History                 = 

The Keewazi are a very spiritual and "traditional" group of Native Americans. For example, they are very mindful and respectful of the tribal god, [[Tomazooma (Manidoog God) (Earth-616)|Tomazooma: The Living Totem]]. The Keewazi have been led previously by Chief [[Silent Fox (Earth-616)|Silent Fox]] and more recently by a younger Chief, Silent Fox's grandson, [[Wyatt Wingfoot (Earth-616)|Wyatt Wingfoot]]. Wyatt Wingfoot's association with close his friend the [[Jonathan Storm (Earth-616)|Human Torch (Johnny Storm]]) has led to the tribe to have numerous encounters with the Torch, and his team-mates the [[Fantastic Four (Earth-616)|Fantastic Four]].
